title: (digimob) Occult Mob's Submissions Digest #22
description:
Occult.digital.mobilization (Digimob) brings you reader submissions and content not included in our mega-torrents.


This torrent represents a work of LOVE. All texts so far gathered, as well as all future gatherings aim at exposing interested students to occult information.

Future releases will include submissions from users like YOU.

For some of us, the time has come to mobilize. If you have an interest in assisting in this process - we all have strengths to bring to the table - please email occult.digital.mobilization @ gmail . com.  

What are you waiting for?  Complacency serves the old gods.

Crowley - Amrita, Crime of the de l&#039;Enfant Jesus, Formula of the Magick of Light, The Amalantrah Working, The Powers of Number, The Abuldiz Working, On the Cefalu Paintings
